      "text": "Here is how I think merging new animals can work. Anyone who plays the game from a logged in origin will be prompted for new animals. This will be recorded along with the path of yes/no answers that lead to the new question. New paths will be merged with other new animals and saved into that origin's animal-guessing-game asset folder. Future versions of the game will read all of these files in order to build decision trees with multiple yes and no choices. A moderator (me?) will merge available trees and add Wikimedia Commons images as appropriate."
